{"tid":2115210,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"可以既話，想同屋企人少接觸（呻","createTime":"2020-07-19T10:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T01:58:16.000Z","uid":271514,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2cd8a6016854db7bd0fd866c1314048297ac3d","tid":2115210,"uid":271514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"以前仲可以話開OT<br />\n或者食夜晚再係街度行嚟行去到十一二點先返歸<br />\n<br />\n家下WFH又冇得出街食搞到日日係屋企<br />\n<br />\n同兩老朝見口晚見面<br />\n日日都睇我唔順眼係度嘈<br />\n就算唔講嘢都可以俾人挑剔話:<br />\n<br />\n我同你溝通，你唔出聲係咩意思<br />\n<br />\n打下機消磨時間又俾人話打機中毒<br />\n<br />\n冇房所以冇得避係房<br />\n佢地話我冇病所以成日將啲藥都俾屋企人揼咗去垃圾房<br />\n要自己去垃圾袋度揾<br />\n<br />\n人工又唔夠我出去租地方住<br />\n<br />\n（人蠢又癡咗線，讀唔成書）<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問出街唔怕肺炎？<br />\n<br />\n我怕<br />\n但最怕都係父母<br />\n由細到大佢哋所做成既恐懼 到而家都係揮之不去<br />\n<br />\n上嚟呻下幾句，多謝你睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d140b19686b7023dd100f6d82be4cc212f7f83","tid":2115210,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:03:15.000Z","msg":"）閂返門啊！！！！！！"},{"pid":"b8e447f85713e7d38902c1c590aca8da43b5f5d4","tid":2115210,"uid":265818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"i know that feeling, brother~"},{"pid":"70383738f44afc9503fb3e616219fbf2bfa2563e","tid":2115210,"uid":326825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:35:41.000Z","msg":"排左公屋未"},{"pid":"445a6d8cfe6c36a1285b3c9c66ae145c01a02f14","tid":2115210,"uid":271514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70383738f44afc9503fb3e616219fbf2bfa2563e","tid":2115210,"uid":326825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:35:41.000Z","msg":"排左公屋未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:44:28.000Z","msg":"排咗，但應該成世唔使上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b78508b46626d8cda05ae5916fb8d968148997","tid":2115210,"uid":154400,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-